<title>
Transmission Warning Light Check (Non-Euro-OBD Model)
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition “ON”.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that transmission warning light (1) lights for about 2 sec. and then goes OFF. If anything faulty is found, refer to 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B5104050">Transmission Warning Light Does Not Come ON with Ignition “ON” (Non-Euro-OBD Model)</intxref>
 or 
<intxref refid = "AENAP70B5104051">Transmission Warning Light Remains ON with Ignition “ON” (Non-Euro-OBD Model)</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</s1>
